{
  "_doc": "Apply: gh api -X PUT repos/goldr0g3r/lotusgift/branches/main/protection --input infrastructure/github/branch-protection.json -H 'Accept: application/vnd.github+json'. See infrastructure/github/README.md for the full apply runbook.",
